description:
Speaker: Tilman Krokotsch

Track:PyData
PyTorch makes developing, training and debugging deep neural networks convenient. Learn how to export your trained model using its just-in-time (JIT) compiler to hide your network architecture, minimize code dependencies and use it in the C++ API.

Recorded at the PyConDE & PyData Berlin 2019 conference.
https://pycon.de

More details at the conference page: https://de.pycon.org/program/8N37P9
Twitter:  https://twitter.com/pydataberlin
Twitter:  https://twitter.com/pyconde
